Kaylee, come on.
Not too far from the side.

287
00:27:31,838 --> 00:27:34,665
Throw the ball, Pop-Pop.

288
00:27:38,726 --> 00:27:40,986
When are we going home?

289
00:27:40,988 --> 00:27:42,783
What?

290
00:27:42,952 --> 00:27:44,813
You don't like it here?

291
