I guess.

295
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:56,159
You guess? You guess? Well...

296
00:27:56,161 --> 00:27:58,123
You want to come out of there?

297
00:27:58,125 --> 00:27:58,755
No! I'm staying.

298
00:27:58,757 --> 00:28:01,450
Well, you want me to come
in there and get you?

299
00:28:01,452 --> 00:28:04,179
I can't have you in
a pool that's only "okay."

300
00:28:04,181 --> 00:28:06,608
It's good! It's good!

301
00:28:10,303 --> 00:28:12,131
You sure? You sure?

302
00:28:12,133 --> 00:28:14,427
I'm sure!

303
00:28:54,458 --> 00:28:57,117
Kaylee, honey,
it's time to come out now.

304
00:28:57,119 --> 00:28:58,681
Just a few more minutes!

305
00:28:58,683 --> 00:29:00,744
No. You do what Pop-Pop says.

306
00:29:00,746 --> 00:29:05,070
Come on, baby, before
you turn into a prune.

307
00:30:39,271 --> 00:30:40,334
Miss?

308
00:30:40,336 --> 00:30:41,731
The gentleman
would like me to let

309
00:30:41,733 --> 00:30:44,293
you know that your
next drink is on him.

310
00:30:45,093 --> 00:30:47,487
Just let me know
when you're ready.

311
00:31:13,842 --> 00:31:15,737
I'm ready.

312
